author: COMSOL
description: This tutorial example shows how to use the Electric Currents, Layered Shell interface together with the Magnetic Field interface to estimate the resistance and inductance of a planar PCB coil in the stationary regime. Typical applications for such a device spans from energy harvesting to wireless recharging.
